<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> that’s the way it goes • that’s the way to go</xh5><p> <i>that’s the way it goes—</i>that’s the way things happen: <u>That’s the way it goes</u> in any kind of criminal conspiracy to hide the truth. More and more people become involved, more and more crimes are committed to hide an initial truth.</p><p><i>that’s the way to go</i>—(also: way to go) is used as an encouragement to proceed with the chosen plan or process: Either I’m going to think about it every day or I’m just going to try to be positive about it and I think <u>that’s the way to go</u>.</p> </entry>
